Popular porn actress Judith Chichi Okpara aka Afro Candy has accused Nollywood of killing Ada Ameh and her daughter. Afro Candy made these allegations hours after the actress’ death. Ameh was reported to have died on Sunday night at a hospital in Warri, Delta State, barely two years after losing her only child, Aladi Godgift. Aladi, who was over 30, died after an unsuccessful surgery in October 2020.   Fuji House of Commotion actress Ireti dead     Sam Larry disowns Portable over one million boys…     Actress Ada Ameh dies in Delta hospital   Reacting to the unfortunate news, the singer-cum-model alleged Nollywood practitioners killed her and the daughter out of envy and jealousy. She prayed Ameh’s spirit hunts down those responsible for her death. “Na wa oh for Nollywood people! So y’all took this woman’s only child and that wasn’t enough, now she’s gone too? Ah! One needs to be careful cos nobody knows who’s got it out for you, so much Envy and Jealousy, It’s a pity! I pray she hunts whoever did this to her,” Afro Candy wrote via her Instagram page.